episodes.title: UK Scientology's biggest threat: Apostate Alex (LIVESTREAM)
episodes.description:
Today I talk with a good friend and fellow activist Alex Ross (Apostate Alex) about his recent involvement in confronting scientology's in the UK.

You can find his channel and the work he does here:

https://www.youtube.com/@apostatealex

episodes.title: SCIENTOLOGY'S GREATEST WEAPON (LIVESTREAM)
episodes.description: lets talk about the tech designed to hold scientologists in place, overts and withholds, and the security check proceedure we are trained to use that enforces scientology onto its members.
